# Markdown Style

- Use clear headings; avoid duplicate heading text (MD024 disabled in config)
- Tables: use `| Col1 | Col2 |` format
- Code blocks: specify language when possible (e.g. ` ```bash `, ` ```text `)
- Run `npm run lint:md` to check; config in `.markdownlint.json`
